itemDisplayName: Deploy a 7 Node, 3 nodetype Ubuntu 20.04 Service Fabric Cluster
description: This template allows you to deploy a secure 7 Node, 3 nodetype Service Fabric Cluster running Ubuntu 20.04 on a Standard_D2_V2 Size VMSS.
